 Year award is given to the player voted best on [[American football positions#Special teams|special teams]]. The recipient can either be a placekicker, punter, returner, or a position known as a [[gunner (American football)|gunner]].\n\n===Winners===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|style=\"background-color:#FFE6BD; width:3em;\" |*\n|Unanimous selection\n|-\n|style=\"background-color:#CFECEC; width:3em;\" |<sup>\u2020</sup>\n|Co-Player of the Year\n|-\n|Player (X)\n|Denotes the number of times the player has been selected\n|}\n{|class=wikitable\n!colspan=10|Positions key\n|-\n| '''K''' || [[Placekicker]]\n| '''KR''' || [[Kickoff returner|Kick returner]]\n| '''P''' || [[Punter (American football)|Punter]]\n| '''PR''' || [[Punt returner (American football)|Punt returner]]\n| '''RS''' || Return specialist\n|-\n!colspan=10|Class key\n|-\n|'''Fr''' || Freshman\n|'''So''' || Sophomore\n|'''Jr''' || Junior\n|'''Sr''' || Senior\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Season\n!Player\n!School\n!Position\n!Class\n|-style=\"background-color:#CFECEC; width:3em;\"  align=center\n| [[2013 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2013]]<sup>\u2020</sup> || {{sortname|Demarcus|Ayers}} || [[2013 Houston Cougars football team|Houston]] || RS || {{sort|1|Fr}}\n|-style=\"background-color:#CFECEC; width:3em;\"  align=center\n| 2013<sup>\u2020</sup> || {{sortname|Tom|Hornsey}} || [[2013 Memphis Tigers football team|Memphis]] || P || {{sort|4|Sr}}\n|- align=center\n| [[2014 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2014]] || {{sortname|Jake|Elliott}}<ref name=\"2014 awards\"/> || [[2014 Memphis Tigers football team|Memphis]] || K || {{sort|2|So}}\n|- align=center\n| [[2015 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2015]] || {{sortname|Jake|Elliott}} (2)<ref name=\"2015 awards\"/> || [[2015 Memphis Tigers football team|Memphis]] || K || {{sort|3|Jr}}\n|- align=center\n| [[2016 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2016]] || {{sortname|Tony|Pollard|Tony Pollard (American football)}}<ref name=\"2016 awards\"/> ||